items.name: MetaWave-MP3-App
items.description: 🥁 A self‑hosted music library and MP3 editor that lets you upload tracks, manage metadata and cover art, and arrange albums with drag‑and‑drop. Built on Next.js, Supabase, and TailwindCSS, it features theme‑aware UI, batch artwork updates, waveform previews, and easy sharing of public profiles.

items.name: Agentic-AI-Pipeline
items.description: 🦾 A production‑ready research outreach AI agent that plans, discovers, reasons, uses tools, and learns - backed by RAG (ChromaDB + SQLite), streaming UI, and a CLI. Focused on research & outreach, it auto‑builds cited briefings and drafts tailored emails with tool‑chaining, memory, tests, and turnkey Docker, AWS, Ansible, & Terraform deploys.

items.name: MermaidGenie-UML-Diagram-App
items.description: 🗺️ An AI-powered platform (and VS Code extension) that transforms natural‑language prompts into fully editable Mermaid diagrams - flowcharts, UML, mind‑maps, ERDs and more - right in your browser. With built‑in versioning, collaboration, and export options, it’s the “Figma for graphs” that lets teams visualize and share ideas in seconds!

items.name: Boxed-Inventory-App
items.description: 📦 A Next.js & Supabase-powered PWA that turns your physical belongings into a fully searchable, shareable inventory - organize items into boxes, tag and photograph them, and track packed status. With BoxedAI, you can ask natural language questions and get instant, context‑aware answers sourced directly from your real inventory.

items.name: Urlvy-URL-Shortener-App
